2 ways to fix the outliers

1) trimming technique - completely remove/delete the outliers

2) capping - update the age's above upper limit with upper limit value and update the age's below lower limit with lower limit value

# Detecting the outliers


df[  (df["Age"] < lower_limit) | ( df["Age"]  > upper_limit  )   ].shape

